        <updateDate>2013-10-07T20:26:54Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Authorizes the Secretary of Transportation (DOT) to obligate any funds made available to implement federal-aid highway emergency relief for projects arising from damage caused by severe weather events in 2013, without any limitation on obligations for such projects resulting from a single natural disaster or catastrophic failure in a state.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
